formulate a physical answer.

00:51:02.770 --> 00:51:07.950
OK, so the physical answer is
that the harmonic oscillator

00:51:07.950 --> 00:51:13.960
is a singly particle
whose position you

00:51:13.960 --> 00:51:15.300
track as a function of time.

00:51:18.190 --> 00:51:21.690
