again, what you

00:51:41.940 --> 00:51:44.970
will see that the particles
are kind of executing

00:51:44.970 --> 00:51:46.680
a coordinated motion.

00:51:46.680 --> 00:51:50.140
Because you have particles that
were down, then they go up,

00:51:50.140 --> 00:51:51.480
and then they go down again.

00:51:51.480 --> 00:51:54.120
But they go out in
a coordinated motion

00:51:54.120 --> 00:51:56.040
throughout the entire plane.

00:51:56.040 --> 00:51:56.750
How do they know?

00:51:56.750 --> 00:51:59.000
Well, there is a physical
system associated with this.

00:51:59.000 --> 00:52:02.330
